!
!
flow exporter BENOCS_EXPORTER_MAP
 description BENOCS_EXPORTER_MAP
 destination 27.123.215.87
 source Loopback0
 transport udp 2055
!
!
flow monitor NetFlow-Monitor
 description Original Netflow captures
 exporter NetFlow-to-Orion
 exporter NETFLOW-TO-ORION
 cache timeout inactive 10
 cache timeout active 5
 record NetFlow
!
!
flow monitor KENTIK-MONITOR
 exporter KENTIK-EXPORT
 cache timeout inactive 10
 cache timeout active 60
!
!
