!
line con 0
 stopbits 1
line aux 0
 modem InOut
 transport input all
 stopbits 1
 speed 115200
line vty 0 4
 access-class VTY-Access in vrf-also
 transport input ssh
!
ntp authentication-key 1 md5 04765B0406221C432A15551419 7
ntp authenticate
ntp trusted-key 1
ntp source Loopback0
ntp server 172.19.1.1
ntp server 172.19.2.2
ntp server 27.123.212.242
ntp server 27.123.212.243 source Loopback0
wsma agent exec
!
wsma agent config
!
wsma agent filesys
!
wsma agent notify
!
!
end